+
+	/**
+	 * @quiescent: A task is becoming not runnable on its associated CPU
+	 * @p: task becoming not runnable
+	 * @deq_flags: %SCX_DEQ_*
+	 *
+	 * See ->runnable() for explanation on the task state notifiers.
